  Evidence: https://www.clay.com/customers/open-ai

  Anthropic:
  - Before: single major data provider, data gaps, manual deduplication
  - After: 3x better match rate using combination of providers through Clay
  - Cancelled top data provider contract, saved 4 hours/week
  - Used Claude-in-Clay to build custom industry categories
  - Quote (Adam Wall, Head of Sales Ops): "Clay made it really easy to experiment with
